Profile of Clinical and Analytical Parameters in Bronchiectasis Patients during 
the COVID-19 Pandemic: A One-Year Follow-Up Pilot Study.

Qin L(1)(2), Gonçalves-Carvalho F(3)(4), Xia Y(1)(5), Zha J(1)(5), Admetlló 
M(1)(4), Maiques JM(6), Esteban-Cucó S(7), Duran X(8), Marín A(3)(4), Barreiro 
E(1)(4)(9).

Author information:
(1)Muscle Wasting and Cachexia in Chronic Respiratory Diseases and Lung Cancer 
Research Group, Pulmonology Department, IMIM-Hospital del Mar, Parc de Salut 
Mar, Parc de Recerca Biomèdica de Barcelona (PRBB), 08003 Barcelona, Spain.
(2)Department of Medicine, Universitat Autònoma de Barcelona, 08035 Barcelona, 
Spain.
(3)Pulmonology Department, Hospital Germans Trias i Pujol, 08916 Badalona, 
